netiConfigMIB.name: netiConfigMIB
netiConfigMIB.contactinfo: Martin Carlsson Net Insight AB E-mail: martin.carlsson@netinsight.se

configStatusIsCurrentUnsaved.name: configStatusIsCurrentUnsaved
configStatusIsCurrentUnsaved.description: Set to true if the current configuration in the node contains unsaved data.

configStatusCurrentLastChangedTime.name: configStatusCurrentLastChangedTime
configStatusCurrentLastChangedTime.description: The date and time when the current configuration was last changed.

configLocalTableLastChangedTime.name: configLocalTableLastChangedTime
configLocalTableLastChangedTime.description: The date and time when the configuration table was last changed.

configLocalTableNrOfConfigs.name: configLocalTableNrOfConfigs
configLocalTableNrOfConfigs.description: The number of configurations currently in the configuration table.

configLocalTable.name: configLocalTable
configLocalTable.description: Table of configuration files stored in the node.

configLocalEntry.name: configLocalEntry
configLocalEntry.description: Each entry describes one configuration file.

configLocalName.name: configLocalName
configLocalName.description: The name of the configuration file.

configLocalDescription.name: configLocalDescription
configLocalDescription.description: A textual description of the configuration.

configLocalCreatedTime.name: configLocalCreatedTime
configLocalCreatedTime.description: The date and time when the configuration was created.

configLocalSize.name: configLocalSize
configLocalSize.description: The size in bytes of the configuration filed.

configLocalAdminStatus.name: configLocalAdminStatus
configLocalAdminStatus.description: Set to enabled if this is the configuration to be loaded at boot time.

configLocalRowStatus.name: configLocalRowStatus
configLocalRowStatus.description: Note that local configurations are created by doing a backup, see the backup group.

configBackupOperation.name: configBackupOperation
configBackupOperation.description: The backup operations supported: idle Resets the function. writeCurrentToLocal Writes the current config to local storage. Uses configBackupName and configBackupDescription.

configBackupStatus.name: configBackupStatus
configBackupStatus.description: The status of the backup function: idle The function is idle. inProgress A backup operation is in progress. failed The operation has failed. ready The operation is finished and has succeeded.

configBackupName.name: configBackupName
configBackupName.description: The name of the configuration file. Defaults to a string containing the date and time.

configBackupDescription.name: configBackupDescription
configBackupDescription.description: The description for the new configuration file. Defaults to the empty string.
